#: ../../source/administration.rst:2979
msgid "If everything seems correct click 'OK' and the unreceived orders and, if selected, unspent funds will be moved."
msgstr "Wenn alles in Ordnung ist, klicken Sie 'OK' und die nicht zugegangenen Bestellungen und, falls ausgewählt, die verbliebenen Mittel, werden verschoben."

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2982
msgid "Wait until the 'Report after moving unreceived orders from budget X to Y' displays. This will list the order numbers which have been impacted (grouped by fund) and detail if the unreceived order was moved or if there was a problem. For example, if the new budget does not contain a fund with the same name as the previous budget, the order will not be moved."
